Specifically we talked about an arbitrage trade =E2=80=94=C2=A0put on by Ji=
m Chanos among others =E2=80=94=C2=A0of buying APE, shorting AMC, and hopin=
g that that discount will close. The discount will close, for instance, if =
AMC gets shareholder approval to issue more common stock, at which point th=
